      "message": "[Critical] Line 94: The package visibility queries only cover image and video capture, but this change is meant to fix audio message sending as well. On Android 11+, resolving or launching the external audio recorder can still fail if the record-sound intent is not declared in \u003cqueries\u003e. Add the audio recording action used by the app, for example:\n```suggestion\n    \u003cqueries\u003e\n        \u003cintent\u003e\n            \u003caction android:name\u003d\"android.media.action.VIDEO_CAPTURE\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/intent\u003e\n        \u003cintent\u003e\n            \u003caction android:name\u003d\"android.media.action.IMAGE_CAPTURE\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/intent\u003e\n        \u003cintent\u003e\n            \u003caction android:name\u003d\"android.provider.MediaStore.RECORD_SOUND\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/intent\u003e\n    \u003c/queries\u003e\n```",
      "revId": "603488cc5105f52f5599e7ef3619fe024d12ffdf",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
